comments: Adebayo (MIA) sets the pick in Simmons' (PHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Embiid (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Leonard (MIA) on his shot attempt near the rim.
Jones Jr. (MIA) moves along his defensive trajectory and absorbs contact from Embiid (PHI) during the drive.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Horford (PHI) sets the screen in Nunn's (MIA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Simmons (PHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Butler (MIA) after the ball is inbounded.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Embiid's (PHI) non-shooting arm that does not affect his shot attempt near the rim.
Replay review of the foul called on Embiid (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Nunn (MIA) makes incidental contact with Harris's (PHI) upper arm after the release on his jump shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) slides his pivot foot after he gathers the ball.
Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Butler's (MIA) arm that does not prevent him from passing the ball.
Simmons (PHI) attempts a take foul on Adebayo (MIA) but the contact is marginal.
Richardson (PHI) commits a take foul on Nunn (MIA).
Nunn (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Simmon's (PHI) drive to the basket.
Jones Jr. (MIA) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Horford (PHI) after the release on his jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) and Embiid (PHI) make incidental contact with one another during the rebound.
Harris (PHI) commits a take foul on Adebayo (MIA).
